  "detailed_description": "Behind the Backrooms is a Co-op online horror game up to 4 players, where you and your friends will fight to escape from the different levels of the backrooms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-op Multiplayer</h2>Explore the backrooms with a team of up to 4 players to solve puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2>Traverse unique levels based on backrooms lore with regular content updates adding more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088440/extras/f36be1dd17f55623d53b4b75329474ee.avif?t=1734201090\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sub Levels</h2>The entrance is hidden in a normal level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088440/extras/ba22947b032c949d1f5473982a03b4b4.avif?t=1734201090\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Negative Levels</h2>The entrance is hidden in a Sub level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088440/extras/ba22947b032c949d1f5473982a03b4b4.avif?t=1734201090\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
